== Usage
{{{
<<AsciiMath formula >>
}}}

== Arguments

All arguments are passed to the
[[http://www1.chapman.edu/~jipsen/asciimath.html|ASCII Math PHP library]]
and rendered as
[[http://www.w3.org/Math/|Math ML]].

== Example

{{{
<<AsciiMath sum_(i=1)^n i = (n(n+1))/2 >>
}}}

<<AsciiMath sum_(i=1)^n i = (n(n+1))/2 >>

